#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="mn132"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "mn132:0.1"
msgid "Majjhima Nikāya 132 "
msgstr "Middle Discourses 132 "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "mn132:0.2"
msgid "Ānandabhaddekarattasutta "
msgstr "Ānanda and One Fine Night "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p><span class="evam">
#. REF: nya1, pts-vp-pli3.190, sc1
msgctxt "mn132:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard. "

#. HTML: </span>
msgctxt "mn132:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya2
msgctxt "mn132:2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā ānando upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandasseti samādapeti samuttejeti sampahaṃseti, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca bhāsati. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Ānanda was educating, encouraging, firing up, and inspiring the mendicants in the assembly hall with a Dhamma talk on the topic of the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "mn132:2.2"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenupaṭṭhānasālā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat, went to the assembly hall, where he sat on the seat spread out, "

msgctxt "mn132:2.3"
msgid "Nisajja kho bhagavā bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "and addressed the mendicants, "

msgctxt "mn132:2.4"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhikkhave, upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti? "
msgstr "“Who was inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn132:2.5"
msgid "“Āyasmā, bhante, ānando upaṭṭhānasālāyaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti. "
msgstr "“It was Venerable Ānanda, sir.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "mn132:2.6"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha said to Venerable Ānanda, "

msgctxt "mn132:2.7"
msgid "“yathā kathaṃ pana tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsī”ti? "
msgstr "“But in what way were you inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya3
msgctxt "mn132:3.1"
msgid "“Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsiṃ—"
msgstr "“I was doing so in this way, sir,” replied Ānanda. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "mn132:3.2"
msgid "Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.3"
msgid "nappaṭikaṅkhe anāgataṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.4"
msgid "Yadatītaṃ pahīnaṃ taṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.5"
msgid "appattañca anāgataṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "mn132:3.6"
msgid "Paccuppannañca yo dhammaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.7"
msgid "tattha tattha vipassati; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.8"
msgid "Asaṃhīraṃ asaṅkuppaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.9"
msgid "taṃ vidvā manubrūhaye. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "mn132:3.10"
msgid "Ajjeva kiccamātappaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.11"
msgid "ko jaññā maraṇaṃ suve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.12"
msgid "Na hi no saṅgaraṃ tena, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.13"
msgid "mahāsenena maccunā. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "mn132:3.14"
msgid "Evaṃvihāriṃ ātāpiṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.15"
msgid "ahorattamatanditaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.16"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:3.17"
msgid "santo ācikkhate muni. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: nya4, sc8
msgctxt "mn132:4.1"
msgid "‘Kathañca, āvuso, atītaṃ anvāgameti? "
msgstr "(And he went on to repeat the verses and analysis as in the previous discourse, MN 131.) "

msgctxt "mn132:4.2"
msgid "Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃsañño ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:4.3"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, atītaṃ anvāgameti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya5, sc9
msgctxt "mn132:5.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, atītaṃ nānvāgameti? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:5.2"
msgid "Evaṃrūpo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃvedano ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃsañño ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃsaṅkhāro ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃviññāṇo ahosiṃ atītamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:5.3"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, atītaṃ nānvāgameti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya6, sc10
msgctxt "mn132:6.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:6.2"
msgid "Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti, evaṃvedano siyaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:6.3"
msgid "evaṃsañño siyaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:6.4"
msgid "evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:6.5"
msgid "evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ samanvāneti—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:6.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya7, sc11
msgctxt "mn132:7.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:7.2"
msgid "Evaṃrūpo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti, evaṃvedano siyaṃ … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:7.3"
msgid "evaṃsañño siyaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:7.4"
msgid "evaṃsaṅkhāro siyaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:7.5"
msgid "evaṃviññāṇo siyaṃ anāgatamaddhānanti tattha nandiṃ na samanvāneti—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:7.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya8, sc12
msgctxt "mn132:8.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.2"
msgid "Idha, āvuso, assutavā puthujjano ariyānaṃ adassāvī ariyadhammassa akovido ariyadhamme avinīto sappurisānaṃ adassāvī sappurisadhammassa akovido sappurisadhamme avinīto "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.3"
msgid "rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā rūpaṃ, rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.4"
msgid "vedanaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.5"
msgid "saññaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.6"
msgid "saṅkhāre … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.7"
msgid "viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, attani vā viññāṇaṃ, viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:8.8"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya9, sc13
msgctxt "mn132:9.1"
msgid "Kathañca, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.2"
msgid "Idha, āvuso, sutavā ariyasāvako ariyānaṃ dassāvī ariyadhammassa kovido ariyadhamme suvinīto sappurisānaṃ dassāvī sappurisadhammassa kovido sappurisadhamme suvinīto "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.3"
msgid "na rūpaṃ attato samanupassati, na rūpavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā rūpaṃ, na rūpasmiṃ vā attānaṃ; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.4"
msgid "na vedanaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.5"
msgid "na saññaṃ … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.6"
msgid "na saṅkhāre … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.7"
msgid "na viññāṇaṃ attato samanupassati, na viññāṇavantaṃ vā attānaṃ, na attani vā viññāṇaṃ, na viññāṇasmiṃ vā attānaṃ—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:9.8"
msgid "evaṃ kho, āvuso, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: nya10, pts-vp-pli3.191, sc14
msgctxt "mn132:10.1"
msgid "Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.2"
msgid "nappaṭikaṅkhe anāgataṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.3"
msgid "Yadatītaṃ pahīnaṃ taṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.4"
msgid "appattañca anāgataṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "mn132:10.5"
msgid "Paccuppannañca yo dhammaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.6"
msgid "tattha tattha vipassati; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.7"
msgid "Asaṃhīraṃ asaṅkuppaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.8"
msgid "taṃ vidvā manubrūhaye. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "mn132:10.9"
msgid "Ajjeva kiccamātappaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.10"
msgid "ko jaññā maraṇaṃ suve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.11"
msgid "Na hi no saṅgaraṃ tena, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.12"
msgid "mahāsenena maccunā. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "mn132:10.13"
msgid "Evaṃvihāriṃ ātāpiṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.14"
msgid "ahorattamatanditaṃ; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.15"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:10.16"
msgid "santo ācikkhate munī’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: nya11, sc18
msgctxt "mn132:11.1"
msgid "Evaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesiṃ samādapesiṃ samuttejesiṃ sampahaṃsesiṃ, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsin”ti. "
msgstr "“That’s how I was inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc19
msgctxt "mn132:11.2"
msgid "“Sādhu sādhu, ānanda. "
msgstr "“Good, good, Ānanda. "

msgctxt "mn132:11.3"
msgid "Sādhu kho tvaṃ, ānanda, bhikkhūnaṃ dhammiyā kathāya sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi, bhaddekarattassa uddesañca vibhaṅgañca abhāsi: "
msgstr "It’s good that you were inspiring the mendicants with a talk on the recitation passage and analysis of One Fine Night.” "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: nya12, sc20
msgctxt "mn132:12.1"
msgid "‘Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:12.2"
msgid "… pe … "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:12.3"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:12.4"
msgid "santo ācikkhate munī’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: nya13-19, sc21
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.1"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, atītaṃ anvāgameti … pe … "
msgstr "(And the Buddha repeated the verses and analysis once more.) "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.2"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, atītaṃ anvāgameti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.3"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, atītaṃ nānvāgameti … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.4"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, atītaṃ nānvāgameti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.5"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.6"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, anāgataṃ paṭikaṅkhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.7"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.8"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, anāgataṃ nappaṭikaṅkhati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.9"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.10"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu saṃhīrati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.11"
msgid "Kathañca, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.12"
msgid "evaṃ kho, ānanda, paccuppannesu dhammesu na saṃhīrati. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc22
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.13"
msgid "‘Atītaṃ nānvāgameyya, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.14"
msgid "… pe … "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.15"
msgid "Taṃ ve bhaddekarattoti, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.16"
msgid "santo ācikkhate munī’”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: sc23
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.17"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "mn132:13-19.18"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā ānando bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandīti. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Ānanda was happy with what the Buddha said. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn132:13-19.19"
msgid "Ānandabhaddekarattasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

